snippet.title: Marvel Animation's Marvel Zombies - Official Trailer #2 (2025) Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd
snippet.description:
Check out the Trailer #2 for Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies, an animated horror installment to the Marvel Cinematic Universe distributed by Marvel Studios. This series re-contextualizes the Marvel Universe as Earth's mightiest heroes go head-to-head against a zombie outbreak, turning even the strongest of them into undead nightmares. Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

After the Avengers are overtaken by a zombie plague, a desperate group of survivors discover the key to bringing an end to the super-powered undead, racing across a dystopian landscape and risking life and limb to save their world. 
 
Marvel Zombies stars Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd, Florence Pugh, David Harbour, Tessa Thompson, Simu Liu, Awkwafina, Hailee Steinfeld, Wyatt Russell, Randall Park, Iman Vellani, Dominique Thorne, and more. The series is executive produced by Kevin Feige, Louis D’Esposito, Brad Winderbaum, Dana Vasquez-Eberhardt, Bryan Andrews, and Zeb Wells, and is produced by Danielle Costa, Carrie Wassenaar. 

Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

#MarvelZombies #Marvel #IGN

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle | Zenitsu vs Kaigaku Trailer | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
The end is near. Crunchyroll is excited to bring Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle to theaters as an epic trilogy event! Get tickets now! https://got.cr/cc-dsknym

It is the Taisho Period in Japan. Tanjiro, a kindhearted boy who sells charcoal for a living, finds his family slaughtered by a demon. To make matters worse, his younger sister Nezuko, the sole survivor, has been transformed into a demon herself.

Though devastated by this grim reality, Tanjiro resolves to become a “demon slayer” so that he can turn his sister back into a human, and kill the demon that massacred his family.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

Letra:
Siento un vacío muy frío por dentro, mi amor
Cuando te fuiste, te robaste mi corazón
Me quedé loco de tanto pensar y pensar
Me iré al infierno, pero me tengo que vengar
Siento un vacío muy frío por dentro, mi amor
Cuando te fuiste, te robaste mi corazón
Me quedé loco de tanto pensar y pensar
Me iré al infierno, pero me tengo que vengar
Quiero manchar el vestido blanco de rojo
Sé que el altar de Dios es santo, pero, mi amor
Cien invitados, y todos tendrán que mirar
Que nuestro amor va al más allá
Quiero que bailemos juntos
En el cielo o el infierno, pero sin ese puto
El que te ha apartado todo este tiempo de mí
Al inconsciente que hizo que no fueras pa mí
Danza, una danza eterna
Pero me voy contigo, pero nos vamos juntos
Llevo tres noches malditas sin poder dormir
Solo pensando y pensando que eres para mí (que eres para mí)
¡Uh!
Y me despido de ti para siempre, chiquitita
Ahí le va pa todos los que traen el corazón roto
¡Uh!
Y su compa Oscar Maydon
Y Fuerza Regida
Camino lento, me duele la respiración
A mil por hora, latidos de mi corazón
En el pasillo me vienen recuerdos, flashbacks
Prometimos que los dos iríamos al altar
Te quitó el velo, aceptaste y luego te besó
Ya has consumado los votos sagrados, mi amor
Un frío muy intenso se llevó todo mi ser
Ya no hay razón pa estar de pie
Quiero que bailemos juntos
En el cielo o el infierno, pero sin ese puto
Al que te ha apartado todo este tiempo de mí
Al inconsciente que hizo que no fueras pa mí
Danza, una danza eterna
Pero me voy contigo, pero nos vamos juntos
Llevo tres noches malditas sin poder dormir
Solo pensando y pensando que eras para mí
Miro cómo brillan tus ojos
Me resigno a perderte, y esta vez para siempre
Me arrepentí de quitarte tu felicidad
Te dejaré, una familia puedas comenzar
Me despido, me despido pa siempre
Y te deseo suerte y bendigo mi muerte
Se la dedico al amor que nunca funcionó
A la persona que roto tiene el corazón

Though the world seems to awaken, a dark undertone hums beneath the surface. Human belief is life giving… and things long thought dead are stirring. Dreams turned nightmares whisper in the air, ‘Where is Peter Pan? And how can I ensure we are never separated again?’

🦇  The Dark Knight Returns

There’s speculation that Christian Bale could once again don the cape and cowl for a project rumored to be titled The Dark Knight Returns. Inspired by Frank Miller’s legendary comic, the story is said to focus on an older, battle-worn Bruce Wayne returning to Gotham after years in retirement.

This potential film would shift the tone toward a grittier, more operatic tale compared to Nolan’s trilogy. Gotham is rumored to be on the brink of collapse, and Bale’s older Batman may find himself mentoring a new vigilante while confronting old enemies in their final forms. Such a storyline would allow Bale to explore a darker, more tragic version of his iconic role.

While it remains uncertain if Nolan would return in any capacity, insiders believe the project could move forward with a new creative team. If realized, The Dark Knight Returns might stand as a definitive coda to one of cinema’s most celebrated superhero interpretations.

Entertain my faith,

Address my soul,
Entertain my faith,

snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— THE SUPER MARIO GALAXY MOVIE

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Super Mario Galaxy Movie, the Mushroom Kingdom faces its most dangerous trial yet as new rivals emerge from the shadows, threatening to shatter the fragile peace Mario, Luigi, and Peach fought to protect. Wario and Waluigi rise as chaotic opposites to the brothers, forcing them into a battle that tests their bond and threatens to turn family against family. Meanwhile, darker forces stir beneath the surface, and the mysterious arrival of Yoshi hints at an ancient power tied to the fate of every world. With kingdoms on the brink, alliances tested, and enemies unlike any they have faced before, the heroes must confront the price of power and discover whether unity can withstand a storm born from betrayal and ambition.
